data.eml:eml: New lineages of Lebinthini from Australia (Orthoptera: Gryllidae: Eneopterinae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Robillard, Tony, Su, You Ning (2018): New lineages of Lebinthini from Australia (Orthoptera: Gryllidae: Eneopterinae). Zootaxa 4392 (2): 241-266, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4392.2.2
